data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***Seller HIGHLY MOTIVATED, relocating for work, ready for offers. Solar panels paid off at closing***    BEAUTIFUL 4 large bedrooms, 2.5 bath, Energy Efficient home with lots of upgrades! Spacious open concept kitchen, dining, and living room is perfect for entertaining. Upgraded gourmet kitchen with 42" espresso cabinets, granite countertops, convection double oven, glass cooktop, large kitchen island, and walk-in pantry. Large tinted sliding glass doors for indoor/outdoor living leading to the screened in pool with brick pavers surrounding the lanai. Large backyard has plenty of room for family and pets to run around! First floor bonus room can be used as an office, a playroom, or guest room. Private nook area that can be used as a mudroom, office space, or pet area. First floor crown molding, 5.5" baseboards, 9' ceilings, and 8' doors.    Upstairs are all 4 bedrooms with spacious walk-in closets. A huge loft and convenient upstairs laundry room. Extra storage available in garage overhead shelves and cooled attic. UPGRADES: whole home spray foam insulation, low E-3 windows, pre-wired surround sound (inside and out), water softener (2020), kitchen reverse osmosis water filter (2020), solar panels (2021), expanded pavers (2022), aluminum HVAC coils (2023). LOCATION: close to Lake Nona, Medical City (Nemours, VA Hospital, UCF Medical School, Research Facilities, etc.), Orlando International Airport, amazing restaurants, and so much more!
